  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BCTestConstants, ValueGenerator<Producer>

    public class ProducerBuilder
extends InCurrencySiloBuilder<Producer,ProducerBuilder>
    Builds Producer test objects using the Builder pattern.

    Basically, you instantiate this class, then invoke various methods to configure the Producer, and when you're done, call DataBuilder.create(), which will return the configured Producer instance.
